plot: ABC's &"Good Morning America&" presents the News and Information Source of the day's topics and journalism. The 1st Co-Host Team of David Hartman & Nancy Dussault, 2nd was Sandy Hill, 3rd was Joan Lunden, 4th Charles &"Charlie&" Gibson, 5th Lisa McKree, 6th Kevin Newman, 7th Diane Sawyer, and now Robin Roberts and George Stephanopoulos. Plus, all the &"Good Morning America&" team throughout the years to wake up to the news show and entertainment about the U.S.A.   Written by  Ben Hallums
